          <h2>Welcome to Daily Quote Journal</h2>
          <p>Daily Quote Journal is your personal space for collecting, reflecting on, and sharing your favorite quotes. Whether you need daily inspiration or a place to remember the words that moved you, this app is designed to make it easy and enjoyable.</p>

          <h3>Features</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Quote Collection:</strong> Save your favorite quotes in one place.</li>
            <li><strong>Daily Inspiration:</strong> Receive a new quote every day to inspire and motivate you.</li>
            <li><strong>Personalized Journal:</strong> Add notes and reflections to each quote to capture your thoughts and emotions.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Our Mission</h3>
          <p>We aim to inspire and uplift through the power of words, helping you keep track of the quotes that matter most in your life.</p>

